cast.name: 沙奎尔·奥尼尔 Shaquille O'Neal

introduction: NBA star Shaquille O’Neal, better known as Shaq, will face off with several sports figures on his just revealed reality series titled “Shaq Vs.”.The show, premiering on ABC August 18, will pit the longtime NBA athlete against figures including Michael Phelps, Oscar de La Hoya, and Kerri Walsh. But, Shaq’s most interesting opponent booked for the series is Serena Williams !Like his other co-stars/athletes, including Phelps who Shaq will swim against in the first episode, Williams will likely face off with Shaq on home turf = the tennis court… It will be interesting to see who wins that match… Shaq Vs. Wimbledon champ Serena Williams…“Shaq Vs.” is slated to air on ABC with at least six episodes confirmed, including a football based episode with Pittsburgh quarterback Ben Roethlisberger.
